title: Great!
text: Stunning views! A few stops, great experience, very helpful driver too. We were not able to make all the stops since it was a large group and people kept turning up late, nonetheless a great experience.
place: Great Ocean Road 12 Apostles Reverse Tour

title: Amazing
text: Unforgettable experience, couldn't visit all the sights on the program due to the tide, but still it was unbelievable.

title: nice
text: A very nice experience for those interested in history. expect to spend a few hours walking around and exploring. It was a bit too hot in June when I was there, so don't forget to bring water.

title: decent mall
text: A decent mall, although the parking is a bit confusing. I went there for the visa application center.
